        <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
            <head>Scope and Content Note</head>
            <p>Typescript, from a tape recording, of Heffner's experiences as manager of the Empire
                Ranch, as told to Charles U. Pickrell, Tucson, Ariz., 1960. Accompanied by a letter
                of transmittal from Pickrell, dated Sept. 2, 1961.</p>
        </scopecontent>
        
        
